      "content": "i mean i know i should call them but i have zero time this week cause of work and my doctor is hard to reach. it's probably just because i've been dehydrated, right? if i just drink like a gallon of water a day and take some ginger for the nausea, it'll probably settle down on its own in a few days. you think that's a safe way to handle it while i wait for my appointment next week?",
