      "content": "that's a relief. honestly i was getting really anxious about it. i'll definitely start hitting that gallon mark today. since you say it's the most important thing, should i also try to take an extra dose of my lithium tonight just to make sure my levels stay steady while i'm flushing everything out? i don't want my mood to crash while i'm dealing with the nausea.",
